The first team goes with you

607
00:39:29,900 --> 00:39:32,160
to lure Immortal Master out of Lutai Mountain,

608
00:39:32,160 --> 00:39:33,900
and stall him as long as you can.

609
00:39:33,900 --> 00:39:36,900
The second team stays in the North Abyss and takes Mr. Kong Ming

610
00:39:36,900 --> 00:39:39,960
as the leader for reinforcements.

611
00:39:39,960 --> 00:39:43,140
The third team goes to the south with me

612
00:39:43,140 --> 00:39:47,380
to Immortal Master Mansion and save all the innocent immortals being trapped.

613
00:39:47,380 --> 00:39:49,320
Chang Yi, what a bad plan you proposed.

614
00:39:49,320 --> 00:39:52,760
If we're going to fight, we shall unite and work together.

615
00:39:52,760 --> 00:39:55,940
Though now the number of us is growing,

616
